Error Handling#

Handle errors appropriately when working with Polygon accounts:

import {
  BloqueValidationError,
  BloqueNotFoundError,
  BloqueAuthenticationError,
} from '@bloque/sdk';

try {
  const account = await session.accounts.polygon.create({
    metadata: {
      project: 'my-dapp',
