SDK Structure#

After connecting to a user session, you have access to these clients:

const session = await bloque.connect(); // apiKey auth (no alias)
// or: await bloque.connect('@alice')   // originKey auth

// Available clients
session.accounts    // Account management (cards, virtual, bancolombia, breb)
